																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">14</div> <div class="vers-content">Then Daniel inquired concerning the law and the sentence, of Arioch the general of the kingâ€™s army, who was gone forth to kill the wise men of Babylon.</div></div></td>
																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">14</div> <div class="vers-content">Arioch it was, the captain of the kingâ€™s guard, that was commissioned to rid Babylon of all its wise men, and from him Daniel would have the why and wherefore of it;</div></div></td>
